1504.name: SG CrMo5
1504.Applications: Mainly used in pipeline, apparatus and boiler application. This alloy is specialy intended for high integrity structural service at elevated temperature.
1504.Suitable_For: A213 Grade T5, A217 Grade C5, A335 Grade P5, GX12CrMo5 (1.7362), X12CrMo5 (1.7363), Upto 1180 MPa
